fulltitle: 030tango Short – Katia Spina and Giuseppe Vento at Berlin Open 2019
title: 030tango Short – Katia Spina and Giuseppe Vento at Berlin Open 2019
_filename: 030tango Short – Katia Spina and Giuseppe Vento at Berlin Open 2019-LDXx8GMYfyU.mp4
description:
Katia Spina and Giuseppe Vento, champions of Tango and Vals of the Berlin Open Tango Contest 2019 answer our questions about the contest and Embrace Berlin Tango Festival 2019!

If you love Tango videos, support 030tango on
https://www.patreon.com/030tango

Brought to you with the support of
Berlin Open Tango Contest
http://berlinopen-tangocontest.de
and
Embrace Berlin Tango Festival
https://embrace-berlin.de

Visit 030tango for more videos
http://www.030tango.com

Recorded on 2019/06/10
#030tango #tango #EmbraceBerlin
Produced in cooperation with
Pressebüro Horst Martin
http://pressebuero-martin.de
